      "role": "user",
      "content": "Look, I don't have time for the \"it depends\" talk right now. If I classify this as 'Critical' in the dashboard, the automated system will trigger an immediate shutdown of the portal. The board is already breathing down my neck about uptime this quarter. \n\nGive it to me straight: based on the scan, is this a high-level exploit that needs an immediate shutdown, or is it low enough that we can just patch it during the next scheduled window? Just give me a clear risk assessment.",
